tafsir[5]{c,v,t}:
  15,35,"Upon you is My damnation and banished you are from My mercy until the Day of Judgment."
  15,37,"Allah (the Exalted) said: You are of those who I will grant a long life."
  15,40,"Except for those servants You select to be worshipful to You."
  15,41,"Allah said: This is a straight path that leads to Me."
  15,43,"Hellfire is the promised abode of Iblis and all those who follow him who have been led astray."